{
  "id": "adv_bond_ngs_01_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "お風呂気持ち良かった～……あれ？\n机の上にあるのって、渚ちゃんの日記かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The bath felt good~ …huh?\nIs that on the desk‚ Nagisa-chan's diary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、開きっぱなしになってるよ\n閉じといてあげない……と……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ diary is open\nI have to close… it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6587979316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "『――4月1日、今日も琴乃ちゃんが可愛い。新学期に\nうきうきしてるみたいで、お喋りの声も楽しそう』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"――April 1st‚ Kotono-chan is cute today‚ too. She seems excited about\nthe new semester‚ and her voice sounds fun\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8553288141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "『――4月2日、去年の教科書を間違えて持って来た\n琴乃ちゃん。可愛い。照れ顔のポイント高い』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"――April 2nd‚ Kotono-chan brought last year's textbook\nby mistake. So cute. The shy face has a big points\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3996591567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9148.4582901
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12633.674176700002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "4月3日、4日、5日……ほとんど毎日書いてる！\n全部が琴乃ちゃんの可愛いところについてだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "April 3rd‚ 4th‚ 5th… she writes almost every day!\nIt's all about how cute Kotono-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5481174468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……ええっ、こんなことまで！？\nあはは、琴乃ちゃん、おもしろーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What? Even something like this!?\nAhaha‚ Kotono-chan‚ that's funー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7284799575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7226524988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うわああああ！　びっくりした！　渚ちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wowwww! What a surprise! Nagisa-chan!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1338160275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。驚き過ぎだよ\nあ、その日記……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ You're so suprised\nAh‚ that diary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2244175353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと～……ごめん！\nつい手に取ったら、読むのが止まらなくなっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Umm~… sorry!\nOnce I picked it up‚ I couldn't stop reading",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6543266374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……どうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6457778054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ……感想？　えっとねー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Ah… appreciation? Wellー…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3522156395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの可愛いがぎゅっと詰まってて面白かった！\n知らなかった魅力がいっぱいあるんだなーって思ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was fun and full of Kotono-chan's cuteness!\nI thought there were a lot of charms I didn't know about",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3433720904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと？　伝わって良かった～！\n『毎日琴乃ちゃん観察日記』、作ったかいがあったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I'm glad it got across~!\n\"Daily Kotono-chan Observation Diary\"‚ was worth making",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3791768389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "特にオススメは六月の相合傘で、肩が触れた時\nちょっと照れるところが可愛くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Specially recommend is that in June‚ when we share an umbrella‚\nit's cute how she gets a little shy when our shoulders touch",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8730318067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "興味を持ってくれた芽衣ちゃんに、もっと琴乃ちゃんの\n可愛いところを教えてあげたいな。早速今からどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to teach Mei-chan‚ who has shown interest‚ more of\nKotono-chan's cuteness. How about right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3045737581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "き、聞きたいのはやまやまなんだけど……もう寝なきゃ\nほら！　明日も朝からお仕事だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I really want to hear it… go to sleep now\nLook! I have work tomorrow morning‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9211040494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それならいいこと考えた！\n芽衣ちゃんが寝るまで、子守歌がわりに教えてあげる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ then I have a good idea!\nUntil Mei-chan falls asleep‚ I'll teach you a lullaby instead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.820650768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんが琴乃ちゃんの魅力に興味を持ってくれた\nのが嬉しくて。まずは中学のエピソードから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad that Mei-chan was interested in\nKotono-chan's charm. First‚ let's start with the middle school episode――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6623059907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "わわ、渚ちゃんの目が本気だ……！\nこれは絶対寝かせてくれないな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wah wah‚ Nagisa-chan's eyes are so serious…!\nThis will never let me sleep~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6944652555,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}